{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was, strangely enough, that what set me off in that direction was the Korean war in 1950.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, there's no end to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, there is no peace in this world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is no-- you just live one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't-- don't bother to plan ahead of time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That doesn't mean I wouldn't plan ahead of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I mean, still, live your-- try to live your day as good as you can every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and this had affected me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was I able to follow through?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably not very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it still-- still affected me, my thinking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still will say that's the only way to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you involved in the Korean war at all?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not involved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lucked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was going to be drafted, and I accepted that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was selective service at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was right before the Korean War.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was before the Korean war with Selective Service.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, since because of my hearing in the left ear, they rejected me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I became 4F.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later on, it was, I think, 5A or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They changed it later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But by that time, I was older.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Korean war was-- that was in 1949, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Korean war broke out in 1950.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I wasn't a standby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, I had to report.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they never-- they never called me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I guess I-- I was lucky, because a friend of mine got hurt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anybody who got killed there, a friend, but several friends of mine were in Korea and went through it.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
